high_descs: Stand next to the stove and face the sink.
Walk up to the sink and grab a knife.
Go around the island to the loaf of bread.
Cut the loaf of bread with the knife.
Go to the fridge with the knife.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Go to the loaf of bread.
Grab a slice of bread from the island.
Go to the fridge with the slice of bread.
Put the slice of bread in the fridge then take it back out.
Walk to the trash can.
Put the slice of bread in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of bread from the loaf on the island in the fridge, put it in the trash.

high_descs: Go to the left, hang a right and go to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is in the sink.
Turn to the right, go to the fridge and hang a right, go to the counter where the loaf of bread is.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn around, go back to the bread that is on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge.
Put the bread inside the fridge and close the door. Take the bread out of the fridge once it is cold.
Turn to the right, go to the garbage can to the right of the fridge.
Put the bread inside the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread in a garbage can.

high_descs: look straight to face the kitchen sink
pick up the knife in the sink
go to the center counter top and face the bread on the short edge of the table
slice the bread on the counter top
turn right to face the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and place the knife on the top shelf
return to the center counter top behind you and face the bread
pick up a slice of bread on the counter top
turn right to face the refrigerator door again
open the door, place the bread on the top shelf behind the knife, and shut the door for a few seconds before removing the bread
look to the right of the refrigerator at the trash bin
throw the bread in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: slice a piece of bread, cool it down, dispose of it in the garbage
